{"tid":2383254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記者多番追問張竹君始認紅磡海景酒店爆疫","createTime":"2021-01-27T19:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T20:47:08.000Z","uid":50275,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3dbbe333ef0e425479d5983f61d7a974d291a9d7","tid":2383254,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T19:39:02.000Z","msg":"張竹君27日在疫情記者會上，主動公佈紅磡永明粥店的7人染疫群組詳情；然而在《蘋果》追問才稱，據手頭資料紅磡海灣軒海景酒店有5至6名保安確診，不過沒提供病人的個案編號、接觸史等關鍵資訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支持足君班友呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#武漢肺炎<br />\n【公佈群組「睇心情」 記者多番追問張竹君始認紅磡海景酒店爆疫】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MbI6fV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MbI6fV&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cUybpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=50f759c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MbI6fV</a>"},{"pid":"996bd3ee3d5d9f9c5637c6d9f972427ce5b51db9","tid":2383254,"uid":11148,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T19:48:41.000Z","msg":"君君底褲好黃架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ac204bbf053e7d2a95bc6c61da272a64046ede","tid":2383254,"uid":126317,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T19:50:56.000Z","msg":"嘩⋯隱瞞疫情，基督徒？"},{"pid":"7a41738ff6ad209871ee520e42537f38239977a3","tid":2383254,"uid":126317,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d3ac204bbf053e7d2a95bc6c61da272a64046ede","tid":2383254,"uid":126317,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T19:50:56.000Z","msg":"嘩⋯隱瞞疫情，基督徒？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T19:52:29.000Z","msg":"又係富有中國特色的基督徒<br />\n同林鄭一樣信奉富有中國特色的上帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba